               cdbs (>= 0.4.93~),
               libglib2.0-dev (>= 2.30),
               libdbus-1-dev (>= 0.60),
               libdbus-glib-1-dev (>= 0.60),
               libgstreamer1.0-dev,
               libfarstream-0.2-dev (>= 0.2.0),
               libtelepathy-glib-dev (>= 0.19.0),
               gtk-doc-tools
Standards-Version: 3.9.3
Homepage: http://telepathy.freedesktop.org/
